## 📐 Architecture Diagram — Current vs Proposed

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "Current (Disconnected)"
        A[chat.py REPL] --> B[AutomationRunner]
        B --> C[task_splitter.py<br/>regex only]
        B --> D[browser-use Agent]
        
        E[cli.py --multi] --> F[MultiAgentRunner]
        F --> G[Orchestrator<br/>Ollama qwen2.5]
        F --> H[ExtractionAgent<br/>Ollama phi3]
        F --> I[AutomationRunner<br/>new instance per subtask]
        
        J[AgentMemory] -.->|"writes but<br/>never read"| K[.agent_memory.json]
    end
```

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "Proposed (Unified)"
        A[chat.py REPL] --> B[AutomationRunner]
        A2[server.py API] --> B
        
        B --> C{Planning Strategy}
        C -->|"Ollama available"| D[Orchestrator<br/>LLM planning]
        C -->|"Ollama unavailable"| E[task_splitter.py<br/>regex fallback]
        
        D --> F[Subtask Loop]
        E --> F
        
        F --> G[browser-use Agent<br/>shared browser session]
        F --> H[ExtractionAgent<br/>post-step extraction]
        F --> I[AgentMemory<br/>context injection]
        
        I --> F
        
        G --> J[Key Rotation<br/>with pacing]
    end
```

